headline: Kellanova misses quarterly profit estimates amid US consumer spending squeeze
summary: (Reuters) -Kellanova (K) missed Wall Street estimates for second-quarter profit on Thursday on softening demand for its ready-to-eat breakfast items and snacks including Pringles and Pop-Tarts, as macroeconomic uncertainty pressures consumer spending.
